{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bd0db06e91","title":"“胡风问题可能是宗派斗争”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8493c2f9dd","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"bd0db06e91"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"2e02820ff4","name":"凌其成"},{"id":"34d49dc9d4","name":"杨金奎"},{"id":"5dafc21bd9","name":"花月初"},{"id":"8aff656cc4","name":"上海第一师范学院"},{"id":"f754c2329e","name":"孔令望"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3dd1035182","type":"title","text":"“胡风问题可能是宗派斗争”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd0db06e91"},{"id":"73f1c36df1","type":"authors","text":"上海第一师范学院杨金奎孔令望花月初凌其成","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd0db06e91"},{"id":"345d02b5f7","type":"paragraph","text":"“胡风问题可能是宗派斗争，我对党的处理表示怀疑。我准备在暑假里研究一下胡风的书，准备参加文艺界的争鸣。”（中文科五班学生杨金奎）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd0db06e91"},{"id":"be460afe25","type":"paragraph","text":"“肃清胡风、潘汉年的反革命集团的案件，全国绝大部分人民都参与了这件事，但至今还不见判决书。难道党中央是发动群众向反革命分子斗争，而不让全国人民知道反革命分子的罪状，又不向人民宣布审判过程和结果吗？”（中文科十五班学生孔令望）","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd0db06e91"},{"id":"b21db6a823","type":"paragraph","text":"“胡风是与目前的一些知识分子一样的发发牢骚，胡也可称为一支香花’，政府的反胡风运动搞得太大了。”（中文科21班学生花月初）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd0db06e91"},{"id":"de3faa566a","type":"paragraph","text":"“（说）胡风是国民党的内奸，那为什么没有电台武器在报上相出照片。”（中文科五班学生凌其成）","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd0db06e91"},{"id":"aee0c0f0ac","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《鸣放言论选集》（上海第一师范学院，1957）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd0db06e91"}],"page":{"id":"f51b25a034","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bd0db06e91","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}